            <article class="a-main  " data-article-url="https://www.wired.co.uk/article/chile-quintero-pollution" data-article-type="article" data-article-uid="KXdBLoQD2EQ" data-meta-title="The brutal reality of life inside one of the world&#x27;s most polluted cities | WIRED UK">
                    <header class="a-header">
                        <div class="a-header__wrapper">
                            <div class="a-header__content">
                                    <div class="a-header__tag">


                                        <a href="https://www.wired.co.uk/topic/digital-society-with-vontobel"  class="a-header__tag__primary">Digital Society with Vontobel</a>

                                    </div>

                                    <h1 class="a-header__title">The brutal reality of life inside one of the world&#x27;s most polluted cities</h1>

                                    <div class="a-header__teaser has-bbcode"><p class="bb-p">In Quintero, oil leaks and pollution from heavy industry is taking a heavy toll on the health of local citizens. Now the fight is on to clean up one of Chile's so-called &quot;sacrifice zones&quot;</p></div>

                                <hr class="a-header__separator" />

                                <div class="a-header__about">

                                        <div class="a-header__byline">

                                        <span class="a-header__byline-item">
                                            <span class="a-header__byline-prefix">By</span>
                                            <span class="a-header__byline-name"><a href="/profile/naomi-larsson">Naomi Larsson</a></span>
                                        </span>


                                        </div>

                                            <div class="a-header__date">24 Feb 2020</div>
                                </div>


