                                            <hr class="a-author__separator a-author__separator--date">
                                            <div class="a-author__article-date">Monday 24 February 2020</div>
                                </aside>                            </aside>



                            <div class='a-body__content has-bbcode'>
                                






    <figure class="bb-figure bb-figure--landscape bb-figure--custom bb-figure--internal">
        <div class="bb-figure__wrapper" style="padding-top:66.66666666666666%">
                        <img src="/static/img/tiny.gif" data-src="https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/ZZ1qad0dvgd/crop/405/f/aaakgettyimages-1186307061.jpg" data-srcset="https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/ZZ1qad0dvgd/crop/405/f/aaakgettyimages-1186307061.jpg 405w, https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/ZZ1qad0dvgd/crop/810/f/aaakgettyimages-1186307061.jpg 810w, https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/ZZ1qad0dvgd/crop/1020/f/aaakgettyimages-1186307061.jpg 1020w, https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/ZZ1qad0dvgd/crop/1440/f/aaakgettyimages-1186307061.jpg 1440w, https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/ZZ1qad0dvgd/crop/1620/f/aaakgettyimages-1186307061.jpg 1620w" data-sizes="auto" class="c-image c-image--lazyload "  />
                        <noscript>
                            <img src="https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/ZZ1qad0dvgd/crop/405/f/aaakgettyimages-1186307061.jpg" class=""   />
                        </noscript>
        </div>
        <div class="bb-figure__content">
                <figcaption class="bb-figure__caption"><p class="bb-p">Children playing in front of the AES Gener thermoelectric plant in the Valparaiso region. The The Quintero-Puchuncavi area is one of Chile's &quot;sacrifice zones&quot;</p></figcaption>
                <div class="bb-figure__credit">Getty Images / PABLO VERA / Contributor</div>
        </div>
    </figure>






<p class="bb-p">One morning in late August 2018, Carolina Astudillo was leaving her house in Quintero, a Chilean coastal town just two hours from Santiago, when she noticed a change in the air around her. As she reached the end of the block she was already coughing heavily. She felt sick, a numbness in her limbs. “It was brutal. You almost couldn’t breathe. My throat was sore, my arms and legs felt numb,” Astudillo says.</p><p class="bb-p">It’s not so unusual for residents of Quintero and the surrounding villages to feel like this. Many of her neighbours suffer from respiratory illnesses like asthma. The air often tastes metallic, rather than of the sea. Even the beach looks darker than it should be – instead of shells, the sand is littered with coal spilt from incoming cargo ships. A few dead birds lie washed up just yards from where some families eat their picnics.</p><aside class="ad__main is-hidden ad--article ad--article-rail ad--article-rail-top stick-wrapper ">
    <div class="ad__block stick-element">
            <h5 class="ad__title">Advertisement</h5>
        <div class="da__container"
            data-ad-unit="generic_tag/articles"
            data-ad-zone="/5574/uk.n5574.wired"
            data-ad-lazyload="True"
            data-ad-sizes="[[300, 600], [300, 250]]"
            data-ad-bidding="True"
            data-ad-sizemap="null"
            data-ad-position="article-top"
            data-ad-values="{&quot;pukwi&quot;: [&quot;Vontobel4&quot;], &quot;doctype&quot;: &quot;article&quot;, &quot;uk-wi-tags&quot;: [&quot;Digital Society with Vontobel&quot;, &quot;Science&quot;, &quot;Environment&quot;]}"
            data-ad-placement="ARTICLE_RAIL_TOP"
            data-ad-group="roadblock"
            data-ad-order="1"
            
        ></div>
    </div>
</aside><p class="bb-p">But this time it was worse than normal. Several chemical gases, including methyl chloroform, nitrobenzene and toluene, had leaked from the nearby oil and chemical plants that ring the town. Between September 21 and October 18 that year, 1,398 people were treated for gas poisoning in local hospitals, according to the Chilean Ministry of Health. The residents of the Quintero and Puchuncaví region had been hit by yet another pollution crisis, another industrial accident. </p><p class="bb-p">Just a few kilometres from where Astudillo lives with her husband and children is the centre of Chilean industrial development. It is home to some of the biggest and dirtiest industries: coal power plants, cement plants, thermal power, natural gas. From just one copper smelter in 1964, there are now around 20 different industrial facilities here, built as part of state plans to drive production. The park was meant to be the engine of economic growth to launch Chile into the ranks of “developed” countries – an idea echoed by the West German minister of Economic Cooperation, Walter Scheel, who visited Quintero Bay during the construction of the copper processing plant: “Chile is not an underdeveloped country but a nation in full swing toward development,” <a href="https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=eC1zDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT156&lpg=PT156&dq=Chile+is+not+an+underdeveloped+country+but+a+nation+in+full+swing+toward+development.&source=bl&ots=Lfv2MSaC_z&sig=ACfU3U3a6OKC-XNdNbJp2iRcB0iMWnej5w&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjrpK_k_7znAhV0s3EKHR0rA5QQ6AEwAHoECAgQAQ#v=onepage&q=Chile%20is%20not%20an%20underdeveloped%20country%20but%20a%20nation%20in%20full%20swing%20toward%20development.&f=false" class="bb-a">he said at the time</a>. But this development has come at a cost.</p><aside class="a-sidebar-content">
        <h4 class="a-sidebar-content__title">Read next</h4>
        <ul class="a-sidebar-content__list">
                <li class="a-sidebar-content__list-item">
                        <article class="c-card c-card--portrait-small">
                        		<a href="/article/coronavirus-tracing-apps-privacy" class="c-card__link c-card__link--article ">Coronavirus tracing apps don’t have to kill privacy to be effective</a>

                        	<div class="c-card__obj">
                        		<div class="c-card__obj__header">
                        			<div class="c-card__images">

                        						<div class="c-card__image c-card__image--square ">
                        								        <img src="/static/img/tiny.gif" data-src="https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/6eoazo5aJJA/crop/200/square/f/corona-privacy.jpg" data-srcset="https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/6eoazo5aJJA/crop/200/square/f/corona-privacy.jpg 200w, https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/6eoazo5aJJA/crop/300/square/f/corona-privacy.jpg 300w, https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/6eoazo5aJJA/crop/400/square/f/corona-privacy.jpg 400w, https://wi-images.condecdn.net/image/6eoazo5aJJA/crop/600/square/f/corona-privacy.jpg 600w" data-sizes="auto" class="c-image c-image--lazyload "  />
